um_lt.html">Lumen gentium</a></i>, n. 31: AAS 57   (1965), p. 37.<BR><BR></div>  	<div id="ftn6"><a title name="_ftn6" href="#_ftnref6">[6]</a> Cf. <i>Ibid</i>., n. 33, p. 39; cf. etiam n. 10, p. 14.<BR><BR>  	</div>  	<div id="ftn7"><a title name="_ftn7" href="#_ftnref7">[7]</a> Cf. <i>Ibid</i>., n. 12, p. 16.<BR><BR>  	</div>  	<div id="ftn8"><a title name="_ftn8" href="#_ftnref8">[8]</a> Cf. CONC. VAT. II, Const. de Sacra Liturgia,   		<i>  		<a href="http://www.vatican.va/archive/hist_councils/ii_vatican_council/documents/vat-ii_const_19631204_sacrosanctum-concilium_lt.html">Sacrosanctum   Concilium</a></i>: cap. I, n.   11: AAS 56 (1964), pp. 102-103.<BR><BR></div>  	<div id="ftn9"><a title name="_ftn9" href="#_ftnref9">[9]</a> Cf. CONC. VAT. II, Const. dogm. de Ecclesia,   		<i>  		<a href="http://www.vatican.va/archive/hist_councils/ii_vatican_council/documents/vat-ii_const_19651118_dei-verbum_lt.html">Lumen gentium</a></i>, n. 32: AAS 57   (1965), p. 38; cf. etiam n. 40-41, pp. 45-47.<BR><BR></div>  	<div id="ftn10"><a title name="_ftn10" href="#_ftnref10">[10]</a> I<i>bid</i>., n. 62, p. 63; cf. etiam n. 65, pp. 64-65.<BR><BR>  	</div>  	<div id="ftn11"><a title name="_ftn11" href="#_ftnref11">[11]</a> Cf. PIUS XI, Litt. Encycl.   		<i>Ubi arcano</i>, 23 dec. 1922: AAS 14 (1922), p. 659; PIUS   XII, Litt. Encycl. <i>Summi Pontificatus</i>, 20 oct. 1939: AAS 31 (1939), pp. 442-443.<BR><BR>  	</div>  	<div id="ftn12"><a title name="_ftn12" href="#_ftnref12">[12]</a> Cf. LEO XIII, Litt. Encycl.   		<i>Rerum Novarum</i>: ASS 23 (1890-91), p. 647; PIUS XI,   Litt. Encycl. Quadragesimo Anno: AAS 23 (1931), p. 190; PIUS XII, Nuntius   Radiophonicus, 1 iunii 1941: AAS 33 (1941), p. 207.<BR><BR></div>  	<div id="ftn13"><a title name="_ftn13" href="#_ftnref13">[13]</a> Cf. IOANNES XXIII, Litt. Encycl.   		<i>  		<a href="http://www.vatican.va/holy_father/john_xxiii/encyclicals/documents/hf_j-xxiii_enc_15051961_mater_lt.html">Mater et Magistra</a></i>: AAS 53 (1961), 